name: Lisa Rocha
description: I’m respectful and considerate, I’m not perfect but a work in progress. Things I like to do: camping, boating, fishing, gardening, reading, bike-riding, hiking, shopping and traveling. I enjoy going to the beach, I love Nature, flowers, communing with the ocean, I also find great pleasure in feeding ducks,watching the sunset. I love to relax by going to the cinema, museum, music concerts, comedy shows, I enjoy swimming.
